@base = http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### Quick Test (direct URL)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Quick Test",
  "price": 5.00
}

### Create Item
POST {{base}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bitcoin Widget",
  "description": "A crypto trading widget",
  "price": 49.99,
  "status": "active"
}

### Create Another Item
POST {{base}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ethereum Dashboard",
  "description": "Real-time ETH monitoring",
  "price": 29.99
}

### Create Inactive Item
POST {{base}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Legacy Tool",
  "price": 9.99,
  "status": "inactive"
}
